@startuml
title AI 组织化演进路径

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE

' 演进阶段
rectangle "阶段 1: 工具\nTool" as Stage1 #95A5A6 {
  card "被动响应" as S1_1 #D5DBDB
  card "单次调用" as S1_2 #D5DBDB
  card "无状态" as S1_3 #D5DBDB
}

rectangle "阶段 2: 助手\nAssistant" as Stage2 #3498DB {
  card "对话交互" as S2_1 #AED6F1
  card "上下文保持" as S2_2 #AED6F1
  card "个性化" as S2_3 #AED6F1
}

rectangle "阶段 3: 代理\nAgent" as Stage3 #2ECC71 {
  card "目标驱动" as S3_1 #ABEBC6
  card "工具使用" as S3_2 #ABEBC6
  card "自主规划" as S3_3 #ABEBC6
  card "反思改进" as S3_4 #ABEBC6
}

rectangle "阶段 4: 团队\nTeam" as Stage4 #F39C12 {
  card "角色分工" as S4_1 #FAD7A0
  card "任务协作" as S4_2 #FAD7A0
  card "信息共享" as S4_3 #FAD7A0
  card "协调机制" as S4_4 #FAD7A0
}

rectangle "阶段 5: 组织\nOrganization" as Stage5 #9B59B6 {
  card "层级结构" as S5_1 #D2B4DE
  card "流程规范" as S5_2 #D2B4DE
  card "知识沉淀" as S5_3 #D2B4DE
  card "文化形成" as S5_4 #D2B4DE
  card "集体智能" as S5_5 #D2B4DE
}

' 演进箭头
Stage1 -right-> Stage2 : 对话能力
Stage2 -right-> Stage3 : 自主性
Stage3 -down-> Stage4 : 协作
Stage4 -left-> Stage5 : 组织化

' 四大要素
note bottom of Stage5
  **组织四大要素**

  1. **角色分化**: 专业化分工
  2. **知识共享**: 经验传承
  3. **流程规范**: 标准化操作
  4. **文化形成**: 价值观统一

  **愿景**: AI 社会 + 人机共生
end note

legend right
  |= 阶段 |= 自主性 |= 协作性 |
  | 工具 | 无 | 无 |
  | 助手 | 低 | 无 |
  | 代理 | 中 | 低 |
  | 团队 | 中 | 高 |
  | 组织 | 高 | 高 |
end legend

@enduml
